author: Megan Palin
title: Melbourne CBD shooting | one person shot
text:
A PERSON has been shot inside a building in Melbourne’s CBD. 
The incident took place on Latrobe Street, near the Federal Police building, about 5.45pm today.
In a statement Victoria Police said it was “understood a person received a gunshot wound while in a building”.
“The person has been taken to hospital,” the statement read.
“Police are not looking for anyone else connected to the shooting.”
Police are responding to a shooting on La Trobe St in Melbourne’s CBD. Source: Twitter 
#BREAKING : @VictoriaPolice are responding to a shooting in Melbourne's CBD - one person has been injured during the incident.
— Sky News Australia (@SkyNewsAust) February 6, 2017 Police are investigating the incident.
